org.itsnat.core.event
Interface ItsNatNormalEvent

All Superinterfaces:
ItsNatEvent, ItsNatUserData
All Known Subinterfaces:
ItsNatAsyncTaskEvent, ItsNatCometEvent, ItsNatContinueEvent, ItsNatDOMExtEvent, ItsNatDOMStdEvent, ItsNatKeyEvent, ItsNatTimerEvent, ItsNatUserEvent
public interface ItsNatNormalEvent
extends ItsNatEvent

This interface is the parent of "normal" event interfaces. Normal events are non-remote view/control events like DOM, continue, user defined or timer events.

Author:
Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
